{"tid":423232,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"藝人中的藝人 你永遠看不到IU韓國演唱會的理由在這裡","createTime":"2017-10-03T17:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T13:47:59.000Z","uid":87818,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c034972cf79da26e7389994c40b384536f9120d8","tid":423232,"uid":87818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"2日，演員박솔미(樸素美）通過INS分享了一張《秋日早晨》的宣傳照，並配文：&ldquo;這次一定要搶票成功啊～要八點整按下enter按鈕&rdquo;，之後演員郭時旸回復：&ldquo;我也我也我也&rdquo;，宋慧喬回復：&ldquo;我也是!&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n在藝人中也如此HOT的IU，你現在知道你永遠看不到IU演唱會的理由是什麼了嗎？那是因為藝人也和你搶票啊~~再次感嘆藝人中的藝人IU的國民度和人氣！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DLHFhCAVYAYtGCj?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDLHFhCAVYAYtGCj%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=af5e7462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DLHFhCBV4AA4IhX?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDLHFhCBV4AA4IhX%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=dacc45dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d60214c15133dcd75a63ea421e9b57070f991ce7","tid":423232,"uid":87818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cccf2ccfc28de1975193eed4c624d798c5cf932","tid":423232,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:20:45.000Z","msg":"solo黎講真係紅得太恐怖<br />\n紅過某啲二線團成團女"},{"pid":"fa435c2a9d816e0135c88743fd4d81d223dfbf3f","tid":423232,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:31:41.000Z","msg":"叫經理人直接打去佢公司要飛啦<br />\n仲慢慢同你㩒咩<br />\n宋慧喬開句聲，iu會唔比?"},{"pid":"a27fadca74ef3fe8d8e7eeb136fbac6787f43f3b","tid":423232,"uid":87818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫經理人直接打去佢公司要飛啦<br />\n仲慢慢同你㩒咩<br />\n宋慧喬開句聲，iu會唔比?</blockquote><br />\n傻既，先唔會直接攞飛，唔係同事關係俾人知道就麻煩，禁就一定禁到，睇下有冇人幫手"},{"pid":"4d94f11321